DMS - Document Management System
--------------------------------

Compile under LINUX
===================

For compilation under LINUX you need the following software packages:

- Qt 4.4.x or higher (http://www.qtsoftware.com/)
- SANE 1.0.19 (backends) or higher (http://alioth.debian.org/projects/sane/)

- After installing the SANE 1.0.19 backend or higher
	- Get the svn package from http://developer.berlios.de/projects/dms/
		- svn checkout http://svn.berlios.de/svnroot/repos/dms/trunk dmsystem
	- Change after download into this directory and enter the following commands

		qmake
		make
		make install is not needed


Compile under Windows
=====================

For compilation under Windows you need the following software packages:

- Microsoft Visual Studio C++ 2008 SP1 Express (optional)
    - Windows SDK for Windows Server 2008 and .NET Framework 3.5 
			(Supported Operating Systems: Windows Server 2003, Windows Server 2008, Windows Vista, Windows XP)
			- http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?familyid=F26B1AA4-741A-433A-9BE5-FA919850BDBF&displaylang=en and install it.
			- Download the latest Qt 4.4.x Source Package for Windows (http://www.qtsoftware.com/).
			- compile it and set the path enviroment QTDIR=/your/qt/direcory without spaces

OR

- MinGW
	- Download the page http://downloads.sourceforge.net/mingw/MinGW-5.1.4.exe
	- Qt 4.4.x compiled for use with MinGW
      - Download the latest Qt4 Source Package for Windows (http://www.trolltech.com).
			- compile it and set the path enviroment QTDIR=/your/qt/direcory without spaces

Have you trouble with installation or you found problems in DMS please send to dms-bugreport@lists.berlios.de and not directly to me.
Have you trouble with installation and/or configuration of SANE please send to http://alioth.debian.org/mail/?group_id=30186 and not to me.


